<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>AI 통합 모니터링 — 전체 아키텍처 (기존 + 고도화)</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Apple SD Gothic Neo', sans-serif;
      background: #0d1117;
      color: #e6edf3;
      padding: 28px 32px;
      min-width: 1440px;
    }

    /* ── 헤더 ── */
    .page-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .page-header h1 { font-size: 19px; font-weight: 700; color: #f0f6fc; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .page-header p  { font-size: 12px; color: #7d8590; }

    /* ── 범례 ── */
    .legend { display: flex; gap: 18px; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 22px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .legend-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 12px; color: #8b949e; }
    .legend-dot  { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 3px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .dot-existing { background: #b45309; border: 1px solid #f97316; }
    .dot-new      { background: #1a3424; border: 1px solid #3fb950; }
    .dot-internet { background: #0c1929; border: 2px solid #3b82f6; }
    .dot-intranet { background: #1a1200; border: 2px solid #d29922; }
    .dot-backup   { background: #12100e; border: 1.5px solid #6b7280; }
    .dot-rpm      { background: #374151; border: 1px dashed #9ca3af; }
    .dot-docker   { background: #081e22; border: 1px solid #06b6d4; }
    .dot-plugin   { background: #1a0a2e; border: 1.5px solid #a855f7; }
    .dot-llm      { background: #150f2a; border: 1.5px dashed #7c3aed; }

    /* ── 최상위 ── */
    .main-wrap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0; }

    /* ── 공용 섹션 ── */
    .section { width: 100%; max-width: 1380px; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 18px; }
    .sec-label {
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.1px;
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px; opacity: 0.8;
    }

    /* ── 배포/설정 관리 섹션 ── */
    .sec-deploy { background: #161b22; border: 1.5px solid #1f4068; }
    .sec-deploy .sec-label { color: #58a6ff; }
    .deploy-inner { display: flex; gap: 12px; }
    .deploy-card {
      flex: 1; background: #0d1117; border: 1px solid #1f4068;
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 14px;
    }
    .deploy-card h3 { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #58a6ff; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .mono { font-size: 11px; font-family: monospace; color: #8b949e; line-height: 2; }
    .mono .hl  { color: #e3b341; }
    .mono .ok  { color: #3fb950; }
    .mono .bad { color: #f87171; }
    .mono .pl  { color: #c084fc; }

    /* ── 연결선 ── */
    .vconn { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; padding: 3px 0; }
    .vline { width: 2px; height: 14px; background: #444c56; }
    .vtag  {
      font-size: 11px; color: #7d8590; background: #0d1117;
      padding: 2px 14px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #30363d;
      white-space: nowrap; margin: 2px 0;
    }

    /* ── 현장 섹션 ── */
    .sec-site { background: #161b22; border: 1.5px solid #238636; }
    .sec-site > .sec-label { color: #3fb950; }

    /* ── 3열 그리드 ── */
    .site-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: auto auto;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .cell-internet { grid-column: 1; grid-row: 1; }
    .cell-intranet { grid-column: 2; grid-row: 1; }
    .cell-backup   { grid-column: 3; grid-row: 1; }
    .cell-mon      { grid-column: 1 / 3; grid-row: 2; }
    .cell-right    { grid-column: 3;     grid-row: 2; }

    /* ── 망 박스 ── */
    .net-box {
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px; height: 100%;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    }
    .net-internet { background: #0c1929; border: 1.5px solid #3b82f6; }
    .net-intranet { background: #1a1200; border: 1.5px solid #d29922; }
    .net-backup   { background: #12100e; border: 1.5px solid #6b7280; }
    .net-label {
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .net-internet .net-label { color: #3b82f6; }
    .net-intranet .net-label { color: #d29922; }
    .net-backup   .net-label { color: #9ca3af; }

    /* ── 엣지 서버 카드 ── */
    .edge-card {
      background: #091826; border: 1.5px solid #60a5fa;
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 9px 10px;
    }
    .net-intranet .edge-card { background: #1a1000; border-color: #f59e0b; }
    .edge-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 7px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .edge-badge {
      font-size: 8px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      background: #1d4ed8; color: #bfdbfe;
      padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;
    }
    .net-intranet .edge-badge { background: #92400e; color: #fde68a; }
    .edge-name { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #e6edf3; }
    .edge-ip   { font-size: 10px; font-family: monospace; color: #7d8590; margin-left: auto; }

    /* OTLP 출력 표시 */
    .otlp-out {
      margin-top: 7px; font-size: 10px; font-family: monospace;
      color: #22d3ee; text-align: right;
      padding: 3px 7px; background: #081e22;
      border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid #06b6d4;
    }

    /* ── 존 내부 화살표 ── */
    .zone-arrow {
      text-align: center; font-size: 11px; color: #444c56;
      padding: 5px 0; font-family: monospace; letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    /* ── 서버 풀 카드 ── */
    .pool-card {
      background: #0d1117; border: 1px dashed #30363d;
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 9px 10px;
    }
    .net-intranet .pool-card { border-color: #3a2800; }
    .pool-header { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .pool-label { font-size: 11px; color: #8b949e; font-weight: 600; }
    .pool-count {
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
      color: #60a5fa; background: #0c1929;
      padding: 1px 8px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #1d4ed8;
    }
    .net-intranet .pool-count { color: #fbbf24; background: #1a1000; border-color: #92400e; }

    /* ── 컴포넌트 ── */
    .comp {
      border-radius: 5px; padding: 5px 8px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .comp:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .comp-e { background: #2d1810; border: 1px solid #92400e; }
    .comp-n { background: #0d1f12; border: 1px solid #166534; }
    .comp-name { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; flex: 1; }
    .comp-e .comp-name { color: #f97316; }
    .comp-n .comp-name { color: #4ade80; }
    .comp-port { font-size: 10px; font-family: monospace; color: #6e7681; }

    /* ── 태그 ── */
    .tag {
      font-size: 9px; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px;
      font-weight: 700; white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .tag-new    { background: #166534; color: #4ade80; }
    .tag-rpm    { background: #374151; color: #9ca3af; }
    .tag-docker { background: #081e22; color: #22d3ee; }
    .tag-gw     { background: #1e3a5f; color: #93c5fd; }
    .tag-plugin { background: #2d1f5e; color: #c084fc; }

    /* ── 백업서버 개별 카드 ── */
    .srv-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
    .srv {
      background: #0d1117; border: 1px solid #30363d;
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px;
    }
    .srv-name { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #e6edf3; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .srv-ip   { font-size: 10px; font-family: monospace; color: #7d8590; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .srv-comps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }

    /* ── 모니터링 서버 ── */
    .mon-box {
      background: #0c1929; border: 2px solid #3b82f6;
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 16px; height: 100%;
    }
    .mon-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #e6edf3; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .mon-ip    { font-size: 11px; font-family: monospace; color: #7d8590; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .mon-recv  {
      display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 10px; font-family: monospace; color: #22d3ee;
      background: #081e22; padding: 3px 9px;
      border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid #06b6d4;
    }
    .mon-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr; gap: 10px; }
    .mon-sub { border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px; }
    .mon-sub-e { background: #1a0e00; border: 1px solid #92400e; }
    .mon-sub-n { background: #0d1f12; border: 1px solid #166534; }
    .mon-sub-label {
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .mon-sub-e .mon-sub-label { color: #f97316; }
    .mon-sub-n .mon-sub-label { color: #4ade80; }
    .mon-comps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
    .mc {
      border-radius: 6px; padding: 7px 10px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    }
    .mc-e { background: #2d1810; border: 1px solid #92400e; }
    .mc-n { background: #0d2a18; border: 1px solid #166534; }
    .mc-name { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; }
    .mc-e .mc-name { color: #f97316; }
    .mc-n .mc-name { color: #4ade80; }
    .mc-port { font-size: 11px; font-family: monospace; color: #7d8590; }
    .mc-desc { font-size: 10px; color: #6e7681; margin-left: auto; }
    .mc-tags { display: flex; gap: 4px; margin-left: auto; align-items: center; }
    .mon-note { margin-top: 8px; font-size: 10px; color: #6e7681; font-style: italic; padding: 4px 2px; }

    /* ── Grafana 플러그인 서브 행 ── */
    .plugin-row {
      border-radius: 5px; padding: 5px 10px 5px 12px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      background: #1a0a2e; border: 1px solid #5b21b6;
      border-left: 3px solid #a855f7;
    }
    .plugin-name { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: #c084fc; flex: 1; }
    .plugin-desc { font-size: 10px; color: #7c3aed; }

    /* ── 우측 열 ── */
    .right-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; height: 100%; }
    .infra-stack { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; flex: 1; }
    .infra-item  { background: #161b22; border: 1px solid #30363d; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px; flex: 1; }
    .infra-item.new-item { border-color: #166534; background: #0d1f12; }
    .infra-item h4 { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: #8b949e; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .infra-item.new-item h4 { color: #4ade80; }
    .infra-item p  { font-size: 10px; color: #6e7681; line-height: 1.6; font-family: monospace; }

    /* ── 배지 ── */
    .badge { display: inline-block; font-size: 10px; padding: 1px 7px; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: 600; }
    .b-green { background: #1a3424; color: #3fb950; }
    .b-gray  { background: #21262d; color: #8b949e; }

    /* ── 데이터 흐름 ── */
    .flow-panel {
      width: 100%; max-width: 1380px;
      background: #161b22; border: 1px solid #30363d;
      border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 18px; margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .flow-title { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: #7d8590; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .flow-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 10px; }
    .fi { background: #0d1117; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px; border-left: 3px solid; }
    .fi.fi-e { background: #1a0a04; border-left-color: #f97316; }
    .fi.fi-n { background: #0d1f12; border-left-color: #3fb950; }
    .fi.fi-p { background: #1a0a2e; border-left-color: #a855f7; }
    .fi-t { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .fi.fi-e .fi-t { color: #f97316; }
    .fi.fi-n .fi-t { color: #3fb950; }
    .fi.fi-p .fi-t { color: #c084fc; }
    .fi-d { font-size: 10px; color: #6e7681; line-height: 1.7; font-family: monospace; }
    .flow-group-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.8px; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .flow-existing-label { color: #f97316; background: #1a0a04; }
    .flow-new-label      { color: #3fb950; background: #0d1f12; margin-top: 12px; }
    .flow-plugin-label   { color: #c084fc; background: #1a0a2e; margin-top: 12px; }

    /* ── v2 옵션: LLM 전용 서버 ── */
    .sec-llm { background: #150f2a; border: 1.5px dashed #7c3aed; }
    .sec-llm .sec-label { color: #a78bfa; }
    .llm-change-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
    .llm-change-item {
      background: #0d1117; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 14px;
      border-left: 3px solid #7c3aed;
    }
    .llm-change-item h4 { font-size: 11px; color: #a78bfa; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .llm-change-item p  { font-size: 10px; color: #6e7681; line-height: 1.8; font-family: monospace; }
    .llm-server-box {
      background: #150f2a; border: 1.5px solid #7c3aed;
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px;
    }
    .llm-mon-box {
      background: #0c1929; border: 1.5px solid #3b82f6;
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px;
    }
    .llm-box-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .llm-server-box .llm-box-title { color: #c4b5fd; }
    .llm-mon-box   .llm-box-title { color: #e6edf3; }
    .llm-box-sub   { font-size: 10px; font-family: monospace; color: #7d8590; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .llm-spec {
      margin-top: 10px; font-size: 10px; font-family: monospace;
      color: #8b949e; line-height: 1.9;
      background: #0d0a1e; padding: 7px 10px;
      border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #3b2f6e;
    }
    .llm-spec .sp-k { color: #a78bfa; }
    .llm-conn {
      margin-top: 8px; font-size: 10px; font-family: monospace;
      color: #22d3ee; background: #081e22;
      padding: 5px 9px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid #06b6d4;
    }
    .llm-diagram { display: flex; align-items: stretch; gap: 0; }
    .llm-diag-box { flex: 1; }
    .llm-arrow-col {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
      justify-content: center; padding: 0 20px; min-width: 130px;
    }
    .llm-arrow-line { font-size: 22px; color: #7c3aed; margin: 6px 0; letter-spacing: 2px; }
    .llm-arrow-desc { font-size: 10px; font-family: monospace; color: #6e7681; text-align: center; line-height: 1.8; }
    .llm-summary-row { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 12px; }
    .llm-summary-row .llm-change-item { flex: 1; }

    /* ── 탭 ── */
    .tab-bar {
      display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .tab-btn {
      padding: 10px 36px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;
      border: 1.5px solid #30363d; background: #161b22; color: #6e7681;
      cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; user-select: none;
    }
    .tab-btn:first-child { border-radius: 8px 0 0 8px; border-right: none; }
    .tab-btn:last-child  { border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; }
    .tab-btn.active-v1   { background: #0c1929; color: #58a6ff; border-color: #3b82f6; z-index: 1; }
    .tab-btn.active-v2   { background: #150f2a; color: #a78bfa; border-color: #7c3aed; z-index: 1; }
    body.tab-v1 .v2-only { display: none !important; }
    body.tab-v2 .v1-only { display: none !important; }

    footer { text-align: center; font-size: 11px; color: #444c56; margin-top: 18px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="tab-v1">

<div class="page-header">
  <h1>AI Agent 기반 지능형 통합 모니터링 — 기존 인프라 + 고도화 설계</h1>
</div>

<div class="legend">
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-existing"></div>기존 컴포넌트 (운영중)</div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-new"></div>신규 추가 (AI 모니터링 고도화)</div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-internet"></div>인터넷망</div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-intranet"></div>업무망</div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-backup"></div>백업망 (광주)</div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-rpm"></div>RPM 직접설치</div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-docker"></div>Docker 컨테이너</div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-plugin"></div>Grafana 플러그인 (오프라인)</div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-llm"></div>v2 옵션 (LLM 전용 서버)</div>
</div>

<div class="tab-bar">
  <div class="tab-btn active-v1" id="tab-v1" onclick="switchTab('v1')">v1 &nbsp;·&nbsp; 현재 아키텍처 (모니터링 서버에 Ollama)</div>
  <div class="tab-btn" id="tab-v2" onclick="switchTab('v2')">v2 &nbsp;·&nbsp; LLM 전용 서버 분리 (고성능 서버 확보 시)</div>
</div>

<div class="main-wrap">

  <!-- ══ 배포/설정 관리 ══ -->
  <div class="section sec-deploy">
    <div class="sec-label">배포 및 설정 관리 — 폐쇄망 제약 반영 (SSH Push 불가 → Pull 방식)</div>
    <div class="deploy-inner">
      <div class="deploy-card">
        <h3>📦 초기 설치 (1회, 수동)</h3>
        <div class="mono">
          1. NAS에 <span class="hl">alloy.rpm</span> 업로드<br>
          2. 각 서버 NAS 마운트 후 rpm2cpio 설치<br>
          3. systemctl enable --now alloy<br>
          4. config URL: <span class="hl">http://엣지서버:9090/config/</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="deploy-card">
        <h3>⚙️ Config 변경 (이후 자동)</h3>
        <div class="mono">
          1. 엣지서버 Config Server 파일 수정<br>
          2. 각 서버 Alloy → HTTP pull <span class="ok">(5분 주기)</span><br>
          3. 무중단 반영 <span class="hl">/-/reload API</span><br>
          <span class="bad">※ SSH 불필요 — Outbound 단방향만 사용</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="deploy-card">
        <h3>🔒 방화벽 신규 요청 (최소 2개)</h3>
        <div class="mono">
          <span class="ok">신규</span> ewas1 → mon :<span class="hl">4317</span> &nbsp;(OTLP)<br>
          <span class="ok">신규</span> anl1  → mon :<span class="hl">4317</span> &nbsp;(OTLP)<br>
          <span class="ok">존 내부</span> 각서버 → 엣지 :<span class="hl">4317 :9090</span><br>
          <span class="bad">기존 유지</span> :9091 :3000 그대로
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="deploy-card">
        <h3>🔌 Grafana 플러그인 (오프라인 설치)</h3>
        <div class="mono">
          1. NAS에 <span class="pl">grafana-llm-app.zip</span> 업로드<br>
          2. 압축 해제 → <span class="pl">~/grafana/plugins/</span><br>
